titleStmt.title: Transcription 32: NMS MS 40 (The Black Book of Clanranald)

availability.p: For internal use by the Faclair na Gàidhlig/DASG projects

note.p: The following text appears at this point in the Red Book of Clanranald but has not been transcribed into the Black Book's copy: 'fir lúirg 7 ar sliocht feraghuid a táid fir lí'.
